<p style=3D"margin:10px 0">A strong labor market reduces the odds of Fed ra=
te cuts.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Investors are now pricing i=
n <strong>higher-for-longer interest rates</strong>.</p></li><li><p style=
=3D"margin:10px 0">Treasury yields jumped sharply (10-year yield moved abov=
e 4.5%).</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Higher yields hurt stock va=
luations, especially for high-growth, high-multiple tech stocks.</p></li></=
